7. Termination of online banking agreement:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
:FED.
7.1 Termination of debtor agreement:SKRSLUT.
.br
If the customer's &WEBSYSNAVN. agreement is terminated, the customer's
debtor agreement for Elektronisk indbetalingskort will be
terminated at same time.
.sp 3mm
The customer will subsequently receive printed payment slips.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
7.2 Unpaid electronic payment slips:SKRSLUT.
.br
&BANKNAVN. is not responsible for any electronic payment
slips that the customer has not paid because the customer's access to
his or her &WEBSYSNAVN. has been terminated.
.sp 3mm
Unpaid electronic payment slips are deleted when the customer's
access to &WEBSYSNAVN. is terminated. Please contact
&BANKNAVN. if the customer wishes to receive unpaid electronic payment
slips on print.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
If &BANKNAVN. terminates the customer's
&WEBSYSNAVN. agreement, &BANKNAVN. must
send the customer printed copies of all unpaid
electronic payment slips. This only applies to electronic
payment slips with a payment date within three months of
the date of termination.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
7.3 Authorised but not executed payments:SKRSLUT.
.br
Payments that have been authorised but not yet executed
will be executed as agreed unless the customer cancels the payment
order in accordance with the rules for cancelling payments
established by &BANKNAVN..
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
8. Creditor's responsibilities:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
Creditor shall be liable if creditor causes late delivery
of an electronic payment slip or if the electronic payment
slip is erroneous. In this case, creditor cannot require
any remedies for breach of contract.
.sp 3mm
Please, contact creditor as soon as possible if the customer notices
that he or she has not received an electronic payment slip or
that the payment slip is erroneous.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
